---
// Modularity.astro - Features of the Extenso Cabin and Cargo Space
---

<section id="modularity" class="py-24 bg-white overflow-hidden relative">
  <!-- Subtle background pattern -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-full bg-[#FAFAFA] -skew-x-[15deg] origin-top right-[-10%] opacity-50 pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 mb-6 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-[#DA291C] border border-[#DA291C] border-opacity-30 border-solid rounded-sm">
        Arquitectura Inteligente
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-[clamp(2rem,3.5vw,3rem)] leading-[1.1] font-bold text-[#3B3938] mb-6">
        Gana Espacio. <br class="md:hidden"/>Multiplica Posibilidades.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-[1.125rem] text-[#646464] leading-relaxed">
        Equipada con la exclusiva Cabina Extenso®, Berlingo Van se transforma en tu oficina móvil y en el aliado perfecto para transportar cargas extra-largas.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Modularity Grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
      
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="group bg-[#F8F9FA] p-8 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-black/5">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white flex items-center justify-center text-[#DA291C] shadow-sm mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-[#3B3938] mb-3">Cabina Extenso®</h3>
        <p class="text-[14px] text-[#646464] leading-relaxed">
          Asiento de acompañante plegable para transportar objetos de hasta 3,44 metros de largo sin comprometer la seguridad.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="group bg-[#F8F9FA] p-8 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-black/5 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white flex items-center justify-center text-[#DA291C] shadow-sm mb-6 relative z-10">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-[#3B3938] mb-3 relative z-10">Mesa Giratoria</h3>
        <p class="text-[14px] text-[#646464] leading-relaxed relative z-10">
          El respaldo del asiento central se abate convirtiéndolo en una mesa de trabajo ideal para tu laptop o documentos.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="group bg-[#F8F9FA] p-8 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-black/5">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white flex items-center justify-center text-[#DA291C] shadow-sm mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 8h14M5 8a2 2 0 110-4h14a2 2 0 110 4M5 8v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V8m-9 4h4"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-[#3B3938] mb-3">Volumen de Carga</h3>
        <p class="text-[14px] text-[#646464] leading-relaxed">
          Hasta 4,4 m³ de volumen útil y 1.000 kg de carga útil, con compuertas traseras simétricas con apertura de 180°.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Wide Feature Image -->
    <div class="mt-16 w-full h-[400px] rounded-lg overflow-hidden relative">
      <img src="/citroen-berlingo/images/gallery-cargo.png" alt="Capacidad de carga Citroën Berlingo" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"/>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/20 to-transparent"></div>
      
      <!-- Overlay Text -->
      <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-8 right-8 text-white">
        <h4 class="text-[24px] font-bold mb-2">Diseñada para Cargar. Construida para Durar.</h4>
        <p class="text-white/80 max-w-xl text-[14px]">La zona de carga incluye anillas de amarre de serie e iluminación LED opcional, maximizando la manipulación segura de la mercancía incluso de noche.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
